{"tid":1999811,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港共危害中共安全 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-05-03T12:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T12:09:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4339664b2857b9b447bb211a44d2a1cd1fffcd","tid":1999811,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200503/20911169/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200503%2F20911169%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=e428d5d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200503%2F20911169%2F&h=0a992f91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200503/20911169/</a><br />\n<br />\n港共危害中共安全 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200503/large/1588413331_4fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200503%2Flarge%2F1588413331_4fba.jpg&h=1d03deab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「全民國家安全教育日」截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n四月十五日，中共國家安全日也，中共駐港辦公室主任駱惠寧大聲疾呼說：「香港維護國家安全的制度不完善，是。。。<br />\n國家安全因此更形重要。」香港偽保安局長李家超應聲附和說：「我們須慎防外部勢力藉香港滲透內地，破壞國家安全。」他們要立法剝盡香港民權，就乾脆說清楚吧，何必託言外部勢力。<br />\n<br />\n一九九七年七月之前，香港由英國統治，一任外部勢力進出，香港事務更一由外部勢力主持，不止是「深入干預」。。。<br />\n中共總理周恩來一九五八年告訴英國：「我們希望香港的殖民地位不變，反對香港成為英屬自治區。」一九六零年，中共官員更警告英國說：「貴國一容許香港自治，我們就會毫不猶豫，揮軍解放香港。」可見英治時代，中共完全無懼「外部勢力」。<br />\n<br />\n一九九七年七月以來，香港民猶是也，地猶是也，只是統治者由港英變成港共。偏偏中共這時卻宣布香港是個「致命隱患」，莫非不利「國家安全」的竟是港共政府。。。<br />\n中共中央贊譽，這是什麼道理？也許，在這個時代，一切都不應按道理分析，否則只會越想越糊塗。唯一明明白白的，是中共又假國家之名，行殘民之實。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"5de881f412bbc63ffd26b2435b955a6840fe4d1a","tid":1999811,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200503/large/1588413331_4fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200503%2Flarge%2F1588413331_4fba.jpg&h=1d03deab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由「外部勢力」嘅領導講呢句嘢特別有說服力 直情係自我招認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}